饮用水市场「打水仗」，单瓶低至六七毛，专家「降价并非长久之计」，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "炎炎夏日，骄阳似火。饮用水市场硝烟四起，以超低价格为主导的「水战」已然打响。 近日，农夫山泉通过各大社交平台力推饮用纯净水，9.9 元 / 包的超低价格在市场掀起了一轮新的价格战。北京商报记者走访各大商超发现，部分渠道甚至打出 8.9 元 / 包，折合约 0.74 元 / 瓶。 在长沙多个商超、便利店，农夫山泉、娃哈哈、怡宝等多种品牌的包装饮用水正开启优惠促销，每瓶饮用水价格最低至 0.8 元。在线上，品牌折扣优惠也不停歇。 饮用水市场「打水仗」！7 毛 4 一瓶的农夫山泉，6 毛 5 一瓶的康师傅凉白开…专家：降价并非长久之计 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-d9680d6e2c86222b916bb28876603f7e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/661602359"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/N/Rk/rxk8YDEAMaCTEwOTMwMDUyNiDQ6860BjAAOL8BQAdyCTY2MTYwMjM1OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1721074811.509680", "card_id": "Q_641480626", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 46}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "白人用中国人的方式化妆会是一种什么样的风格？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-67cb3bb3c7f32e7fb617ab91d6ace0d5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/641480626"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI/N/Rk/rxk8YDEAMaCTEwNDgyOTExNSDi+dGtBjAAOL4CQAhyCTY0MTQ4MDYyNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1721074811.509925", "card_id": "Q_661522415", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "肯德基刚进入中国市场时真的是高端吃食吗，有没有亲历者来聊聊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"te